data.description: Short Sale.  Renovator's Dream: Bring your creative vision to life with this fixer-upper.  With three bedrooms, there's room for the whole family. Plus, the large backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, BBQs, and relaxation. Close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and all the attractions Daytona Beach has to offer. Located in a prime area, this property is a canvas awaiting your artistic touch. Please be aware that this property is currently condemned with no access. Buyers are responsible for all necessary inspections, permits, and renovations to bring it up to code. Despite its current condition, the location is unbeatable. Take advantage of the vibrant Daytona Beach community and all it has to offer. Please be advised no offer will be accepted before the required 30 day minimum listing period, this price has not yet been confirmed by the lender.
